        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "We need to use linear programming to optimize our delivery routes and minimize fuel costs.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "The operations research team developed a complex LP model to solve the production scheduling problem.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "Linear programming is a powerful mathematical technique for finding the best outcome in a given situation, subject to constraints.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "Understanding the simplex algorithm is crucial for working with large-scale LP problems.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "This logistics challenge can be effectively modeled and solved using linear programming.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "line printer",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "Remember those old line printers? The sound was deafening, but they churned out reports like nobody's business!",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "Back in the day, getting a printout from the mainframe involved waiting for the line printer to finish its job.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "We still have a few legacy systems that rely on a line printer for batch processing.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "It's amazing how far printing technology has come since the era of the noisy, dot-matrix line printer.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "laser printer",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "I'm looking for a new laser printer for my home office; speed and print quality are my top priorities.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "This new office model is a duplex laser printer, which is great for saving paper.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "For professional-looking documents, you can't beat the crisp output of a good laser printer.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "Hey, can you send that PDF to the laser printer down the hall? Mine's out of toner.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "Considering the volume of printing I do, a laser printer is definitely more cost-effective in the long run.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 5,
        "gloss": "Liberal Party",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
